snippet.title: Nioh 2 - TGS 2019 Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/nioh-2?emcid=or-1s-412983

Nioh 2 launches early 2020.

Prepare for the horror of the Dark Realm with your first look at the samurai adventure’s intense combat in a brand new trailer, just revealed at Tokyo Game Show.
